    <item>
      <title>中国出台新举措促进并购重组</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/china-unveils-new-measures-to-boost-m-a-restructuring</link>
      <description><![CDATA[作为中国政府为提振低迷的经济而推出的最新刺激计划的一部分，中国证券监管机构推出了新的指导方针，促进上市公司的兼并重组。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/china-unveils-new-measures-to-boost-m-a-restructuring</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 24 Sep 2024 14:44:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国外长斯塔默口误 呼吁归还加沙“香肠”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/uk-s-starmer-calls-for-return-of-gaza-sausages-in-verbal-gaffe</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国首相基尔·斯塔默在其工党年度大会上的演讲中无意中呼吁归还加沙“香肠”，这一呼吁严重偏离了他对中东和平的呼吁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/uk-s-starmer-calls-for-return-of-gaza-sausages-in-verbal-gaffe</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 24 Sep 2024 14:03:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>厄瓜多尔打击贩毒团伙的战争重创了该国旅游业</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/where-to-go-in-ecuador-security-concerns-jump-on-surge-in-drug-gang-violence</link>
      <description><![CDATA[每四年举办一次的全球天主教会议本月在基多举行，但受国内贩毒战争阴影的影响，出席人数比计划减少了 25％。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/where-to-go-in-ecuador-security-concerns-jump-on-surge-in-drug-gang-violence</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 24 Sep 2024 14:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>斯塔默称他已准备好接受不受欢迎的挑战</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/starmer-says-he-s-ready-to-be-unpopular-to-tackle-uk-challenges</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国首相基尔·斯塔默表示，他将做出“艰难的长期决定”来改革英国，修复该国的公共财政。这是自英国工党在 7 月大选中获胜以来，他首次在工党年度会议上发表讲话。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/starmer-says-he-s-ready-to-be-unpopular-to-tackle-uk-challenges</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 24 Sep 2024 13:55:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>意大利准备出售邮政股份以筹集约 24 亿欧元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/italy-preparing-to-sell-poste-stake-to-raise-about-2-4-billion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，意大利总理乔治亚·梅洛尼 (Giorgia Meloni) 准备出售意大利邮政公司 (Poste Italiane SpA) 高达 15% 的股份，作为旨在削减该国巨额债务的私有化举措的一部分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/italy-preparing-to-sell-poste-stake-to-raise-about-2-4-billion</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 24 Sep 2024 13:47:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>联合国秘书长谴责世界没有规则 关注以色列和俄罗斯</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/un-chief-laments-world-without-rules-with-eye-on-israel-russia</link>
      <description><![CDATA[联合国秘书长安东尼奥·古特雷斯哀叹这个世界没有规则，并毫不掩饰地指责以色列和俄罗斯践踏国际法。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/un-chief-laments-world-without-rules-with-eye-on-israel-russia</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 24 Sep 2024 13:16:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
